• A person can maintain approx. 150 active relationships at a single time.

• We spend approximately 60% of our social efforts around 15 people.

#InternationalDayofFriendship #Oxford #OxfordUni #OxfordUniversity

node.title: How many friends is too many?

May be an image of 2 people and text that says 'beaaม Of a study of 200 million Facebook users, 28% (56.3 million) revealed sexuality- related information. May be an image of one or more people, sky and text that says 'The study found that women in their 20s and early 30s are twice as likely as older women to identify as bisexual. NEW REPORTS: Reaching #NetZero will mean tackling the harder-to-reach 20% of emissions. 

It also means extracting at least 5% extra to cover emissions that we can’t get rid of. Together, this is known as the #Final25. 

Read our latest reports on how it can be done: ox.ac.uk/news
